Source.Name: pygments
Source.Summary: Pygments is a syntax highlighting package written in Python
Source.Description: Pygments is a generic syntax highlighter written in Python that supports over 500 languages and text formats, for use in code hosting, forums, wikis or other applications that need to prettify source code.
